H0.text: A gymnophobia sufferer fears what. Public Speaking

H1.text: A gymnophobia sufferer fears what. Exercise

H2.text: A gymnophobia sufferer fears what. Sports

H3.text: A gymnophobia sufferer fears what. Nude

A4.text: Gymnophobia is a fear (phobia) of or prejudice against nudity.

A6.text: The sexual nature of nudity is defined by the gaze of others.

A7.text: In a 21st century, some high-end New York City gyms were redesigned to cater to millennials who want to shower without ever being seen naked.
